testcase.name: Given I am a logged in user
When I navigate to the Clia Labs page
When I click on the "MoCha" section
And I click on "No Template Control" under "MoCha"
And I enter "SC_YQ111" in the search field on "No Template Control" under "MoCha"
And I collect information about the sample variant report
And I click on the sample control link
Then I verify that I am on the sample control page for that molecularId
And I verify all the values on the left hand side section under "No Template Control"
And I verify all the values on the right hand side section under "No Template Control"
And I verify all the headings on the "left" hand side section under "No Template Control"
And I verify all the headings on the "right" hand side section under "No Template Control"
And I verify the presence of SNVs, CNVs and Gene Fusions Table
And I verify the valid Ids are links in the SNVs/MNVs/Indels table under "No Template Control"
And I verify the valid Ids are links in the Gene Fusions table under "No Template Control"
And I verify the valid Ids are links in the Copy Number Variants table under "No Template Control"
